Package: openadds
Title: Client to Access 'Openaddresses.io' Data
Description: 'Openaddresses' (<http://openaddresses.io/>) client. Search,
    fetch data, and combine datasets. Outputs are easy to visualize
    with base plots, 'ggplot2', or 'leaflet'.
Version: 0.0.8.9000
